ation-origin=\"off\">Open developer console (e.g. in Chrome Ctrl + Shift + j)</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">輸入 <code>ng.</code>（通常，控制檯會顯示自動完成建議）</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Type <code>ng.</code> (usually the console will show auto-complete suggestion)</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">試用變更檢測剖析器 <code>ng.profiler.timeChangeDetection()</code> 然後按 Enter。。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Try the change detection profiler <code>ng.profiler.timeChangeDetection()</code>\nthen hit Enter.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-browser\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/ComponentRef\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/enableDebugTools#description\n - api/platform-browser/enableDebugTools#enabledebugtools\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/platform-browser/src/browser/tools/tools.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L14-L41\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/platform-browser/src/browser/tools/tools.ts#L14-L41\n-->"}